            <p class="text-justify">Virgin Atlantic is a British-based airline that was established in 1984 as British Atlantic Airways but it was changed to its present name. The airline operates its services in North America, the Caribbean, Africa, the Middle East, and Asia from its main base at Heathrow, and its secondary base at Manchester. It also operates seasonal flights from Belfast and Edinburgh. Virgin  Atlantic. The airline also has a frequent flyer program to reward loyal customers called flying club. </p>
